title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 11/19 - Friday Feast!
description: PA & Charch at BWWs Apple Valley in front of the Border Battle with Greenbay! Football talkers and fantasy opinions bookend an interview PA did with former MN Wild stud Andrew Brunette, now coaching the Florida Panthers, as his new team hosts his old team tomorrow afternoon!
